<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<a id="top" <p>
Everybody likes to have a little helping hand now and then. What could be better than having a God on your side? But... it's not quite that easy. The Gods won't help just any old mortal who calls for help; you have to give them a little something too.... 
</p>
